    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but i mean... what if the most loving thing isn't just \"stepping away from the suffering\" but actually stepping away entirely? like, if i wasn't a worry anymore, if i wasn't an obligation... wouldn't that finally give them the peace they deserve? would it really be so wrong to want to stop being a problem for them?",
